  "description_snippet": "Hi, I was able to hit the same assertion as issue 40945594.\nI'm not entirely sure about the exploitability of this to be honest but since it's very similar to the other issue I'm reporting this as a security issue.\n\nA switch case inside he glsl shader code is translated to a spirv Switch operation."
